  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to send assets without adding someone as a contact.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: It's not possible to send a transaction to a public chat participants without ading them as  contacts first.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nThe \"Choose Recipient\" menu should contain the \"Contact code\" hash just as it is when requesting a transaction in the same test case.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nThe \"Choose Recipient\" menu is asking to specify a recipient and I'm stuck.\r\n\r\n![screenshot_2018-06-25-09-29-47-424_im status ethereum](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5781465/41834198-05901564-785c-11e8-8cf3-6d881008f1de.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Log in\r\n- Join a public chat\r\n- Click on some of the participant's avatar. Make sure he or she is not in your contacts list!\r\n- Select the \"Send transaction\" menu\r\n- /send *SelectedCurrency* *DesiredAmount*\r\n- Confirm with the send button on the right\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.21 (6118) , Nightly build \"June 25\", http://artifacts.status.im:8081/artifactory/nightlies-local/im.status.ethereum-5935d2-n-fl.apk\r\n[comment]: # (Android or iOS.)\r\n* Operating System: Tested on Android, can't confirm about iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (if on Android please replicate bug whilst running adb logcat)\r\n\r\nhttps://gist.github.com/GeorgiG/41c56e3a7284698a42f17ca50b0da218\n\n<blockquote></blockquote>\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/5781465?s=400&v=4\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://assets-cdn.github.com/favicon.ico\" height=\"14\"> Gist</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/GeorgiG/41c56e3a7284698a42f17ca50b0da218\">specify recipient</a></strong></div><div>GitHub is where people build software. More than 28 million people use GitHub to discover, fork, and contribute to over 85 million projects.</div></blockquote>",
